1. *Rekli* su da će proći još dva dana. (They said that it will take two more days.)
2. *Rekla* je da će završiti zadatak u roku. (She said that she will finish the task on time.)
3. *Reklo* se da će doći još jedan gost. (It was said that one more guest will come.)
4. Oni su *rekli* da će se vratiti u roku. (They said that they will return on time.)
5. Ja sam *rekla* da ću doći ranije. (I said that I will come earlier.)
6. *Reklo* se da će doći u posetu. (It was said that they will come for a visit.)